quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"Ampa s־µ, agyidiefoֽ» no adi nkonim,"
  23,2,"(Agyidiefoֽ») no a wֽ»nya suro anaa wֽ»ber־µ wֽ»n ho ase wֽ» wֽ»n Nyamefr־µ mu no,"
  23,3,"Ne wֽ»n a wֽ»twe wֽ»n ho fri ahuhus־µm (tes־µ nkontompo, at־µm didie, kasa fii, ahohwi bra anaa ade־µ biara a egu onipa ho fii) ho,"
  23,4,"Ne wֽ»n a wֽ»yi Zaka,"
  23,5,"Ne wֽ»n a wֽ»hw־µ wֽ»n mmarima so yie, (anaas־µ wֽ»twe wֽ»n ho fri adwamammֽ») ho."
  23,6,"Gyes־µ wֽ»n ayerenom (nko ara) hֽ», anaas־µ wֽ»n (mfenaa) a wֽ»y־µ wֽ»n dea no hֽ».. Nokor־µ s־µ woi nom na soboֽ» biara nna wֽ»n soֽ»."
  23,7,"Obi a ֽ»bֹ›fri (mmaa a yֹ›akyer־µ mu yi) akyi no, wֽ»n ne mmratofoֽ» no."
  23,8,"Ne wֽ»n a wֽ»n nhw־µsode־µ a y־µde ahy־µ wֽ»n nsa, ne wֽ»n bֽ»hy־µ nso wֽ»hw־µ so yie di mu nokor־µ,"
  23,9,"Ne wֽ»n a wֽ»hw־µ wֽ»n Nyamefr־µ so yie."
  23,10,"Woi nom ne adedifoֽ» no,"
  23,11,"Wֽ»n na wֽ»bֹ›di ade־µ wֽ» Aheman Firdaws no mu, na emu na wֽ»b־µtena afe bֽ»ֽ»."
  23,12,"Ampa s־µ Y־µbֽ»ֽ» onipa frii n־µte־µ a yֹ›asֽ»ne soֽ» mu."
  23,13,"Afei Y־µג€™y־µ־µ no nkwaboa de no hy־µ־µ bea bi a ־µhֽ» dwoֽ» mu,"
  23,14,"Afei Y־µy־µ־µ nkwaboa no mogyatoa, ־µna Y־µbֽ»ֽ» mogyatoa no (y־µ־µ no) namkum, ־µna namkum no Y־µbֽ»ֽ» nnompe (hyehy־µ־µ mu) ־µna Y־µde nnam duraa nnompe no ho, ansa na Y־µrebֽ» no abֽ»de־µ foforֽ». Enti nhyira Wura ne Nyankopֽ»n, ֽ»bֽ»ֽ» ade־µ mu ֶ†bֽ»ֽ» ade־µ papa no."
  23,15,"Afei ־µno akyiri no nokor־µ s־µ mobֹ›wu."
  23,16,"Afei nokor־µ s־µ, Wusֽ»re־µ da no y־µbenyane mo."
  23,17,"Ampa s־µ Yֹ›abֽ» akwan nson wֽ» moapampamu soro, na Yֹ›mmu Yג€™ani nguu abֽ»de־µ no so."